com.brashmonkey.spriter

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.brashmonkey.spriter.Entity

  • public class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an entity of a Spriter SCML file. An entity holds Animations, an id, a name. characterMaps and objectInfos may be empty.
